name: enrich-actionkit-data
description: Augment ActionKit data with county and jurisdiction info

scripts.add-county: rimraf add_county.js && rimraf output1.csv && tsc add_county.ts && node add_county.js
scripts.add-jurisdiction: rimraf add_jurisdiction.js && rimraf output2.csv && cd ../../ && tsc --build power-the-polls-form && cd scripts/enrich-actionkit-data && tsc add_jurisdiction.ts && node add_jurisdiction.js
